<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.9.1/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/infopage.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div id="progress-bar"></div>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div style="display: flex;">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#mission"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</a></li>
                <li><a href="#offerings"><i class="fas fa-gift"></i> What We Offer</a></li>
                <li><a href="#how-it-works"><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How It Works</a></li>
                <li><a href="#values"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Our Values</a></li>
                <li><a href="#team"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Our Team</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="main-content">
            <div class="title-section">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <p>Welcome to <%= appName %>! Learn more about our mission, what we offer, and the core values that drive us forward.</p>
            </div>

            <section id="mission">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission</h2>
                <p>At <%= appName %>, we believe in fostering strong local connections and promoting sustainable, community-driven commerce. Our platform is built to make buying and selling easier, safer, and more accessible for everyone.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="offerings">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-gift"></i> What We Offer</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Buy & Sell Locally: Find great deals on items you need or sell your own goods easily.</li>
                    <li>Trusted Listings: All our listings are community-driven, allowing for safe exchanges.</li>
                    <li>Community Focused: We're here to support local businesses and promote neighborhood connections.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section id="how-it-works">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> How It Works</h2>
                <p>Simply create a free account, post your ads, browse listings, and connect with others in your community. From finding food to housing, <%= appName %> brings your local market online.</p>
            </section>

            <section id="values">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Our Values</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Trust:</b> We prioritize safety and transparency in all interactions.</li>
                    <li><b>Community:</b> Supporting and uplifting our local communities is at the heart of everything we do.</li>
                    <li><b>Convenience:</b> Our platform is designed to make the buying and selling process seamless.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section id="team">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Our Team</h2>
                <p>Our team is passionate about connecting people through technology. We are a group of dedicated professionals committed to building a community where local markets thrive and relationships flourish.</p>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Scroll Progress Bar
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const scrollTop = window.scrollY;
            const docHeight = document.body.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
            const scrollPercent = (scrollTop / docHeight) * 100;
            document.getElementById('progress-bar').style.width = scrollPercent + '%';
        });
    </script>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>